{"tid":158201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE口試考廿四孝　「滌親溺器」嚇窒考生","createTime":"2017-03-16T06:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T04:04:20.000Z","uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4af18ca40da68d0a49348f0bb920890f164cefb6","tid":158201,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:13:25.000Z","msg":"中學文憑試中文科一直被喻為「死亡之卷」，不少牙尖嘴利的考生以為可以在說話能力考卷搶回不少分數，但昨日的口試題目卻驚現廿四孝故事典故題，要考生討論「戲彩娛親」、「滌親溺器」哪個提倡孝道的故事更值得為人子女者學習，頓時考起學生，有考生直言：「個四字詞讀都未識讀」，認為題目太深，學生難以發揮。 <br />\n<br />\n「戲彩娛親」、「滌親溺器」說的是甚麼故事？題目附有解釋，指「戲彩娛親」是指「穿上斑斕的五彩衣裳，裝作小孩形態，戲耍舞蹈，娛悅雙親為樂」；「滌親溺器」則解作「每天晚上都親自為母親清洗便桶」。若非滿肚墨水可清楚解釋故事內容，恐怕亦難以作出精彩辯論搶分。 <br />\n<br />\n有考生看過題目後，直言：「兩個故事都唔識」，應考時「口啞啞」，擔心會嚴重失分；有考生更稱，在解釋「滌親溺器」時，「我講果陣原本想讀「迪」(滌粵音為迪)，但係(同組考生)讀咗「條」，搞到我怯一怯跟咗佢，最後成組錯晒。」有考生則指：「有人話幫母親洗尿兜好唔衞生，唔應該滌親溺器，笑死。」 <br />\n<br />\n其他口試題目還包括「你認為那一種蔬菜更能象徵人生，試談談你的看法：洋蔥、苦瓜」，以及「以下哪一個詞語最適合形容青少年時期？迷惘、反叛、寂寞」、「以下是獎勵要考慮的準則，試按其重要性排優次：公平、及時、適度」。不少考生認為頭兩條題目較負面，「講到好灰。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170316%2Fbkn-20170316105526267-0316_00822_001.html&amp;h=ATNrj3h9NzfGtEnGKGSrnHv8fIApzGXYStiRxh_n2i-Jq_efjV0ALTmKbBcIRylgJuP4pK2JvJrzGjZ6HleD_vgY5zleC2ZdSxDTJRE&amp;s=1&amp;enc=AZNSVAWSuXUh4qUh23vntUqYWeHtD-hCyKbmOq2vOo4lUqr0IyTzSB_FHwY0CHHxkcr9tab_fASQfeCjALiz0kcxFfQKIoJwVhQqRxgN9G9c8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fl.facebook.com%2Fl.php%3Fu%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fhk.on.cc%252Fhk%252Fbkn%252Fcnt%252Fnews%252F20170316%252Fbkn-20170316105526267-0316_00822_001.html%26h%3DATNrj3h9NzfGtEnGKGSrnHv8fIApzGXYStiRxh_n2i-Jq_efjV0ALTmKbBcIRylgJuP4pK2JvJrzGjZ6HleD_vgY5zleC2ZdSxDTJRE%26s%3D1%26enc%3DAZNSVAWSuXUh4qUh23vntUqYWeHtD-hCyKbmOq2vOo4lUqr0IyTzSB_FHwY0CHHxkcr9tab_fASQfeCjALiz0kcxFfQKIoJwVhQqRxgN9G9c8A&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ee29fba0\" target=\"_blank\">https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170316%2Fbkn-20170316105526267-0316_00822_001.html&amp;h=ATNrj3h9NzfGtEnGKGSrnHv8fIApzGXYStiRxh_n2i-Jq_efjV0ALTmKbBcIRylgJuP4pK2JvJrzGjZ6HleD_vgY5zleC2ZdSxDTJRE&amp;s=1&amp;enc=AZNSVAWSuXUh4qUh23vntUqYWeHtD-hCyKbmOq2vOo4lUqr0IyTzSB_FHwY0CHHxkcr9tab_fASQfeCjALiz0kcxFfQKIoJwVhQqRxgN9G9c8A</a>"},{"pid":"4c1ac713b75bcaf5410b8b091f481e200344d18c","tid":158201,"uid":10874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:15:38.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果俾我考中滌親真係下年再黎過"},{"pid":"c1ae02df4190cdc27c75268fd98faab9b5244658","tid":158201,"uid":10045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:18:09.000Z","msg":"下。。。。滌字也唔識讀。。。。"},{"pid":"495c1a4de4872ace042434ec5a644d36481d8389","tid":158201,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下。。。。滌字也唔識讀。。。。</blockquote><br />\n洗滌個個都識讀 但就咁單一個字未必反應到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be51b3394af1311709ca2a36deaf643b3479a027","tid":158201,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"「戲彩娛親」、「滌親溺器」 連內容都唔識真係唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但字面上理解 應該可以估到前者係娛親=娛樂親人 後者溺器=裝屎既野 咁都估到係幫親人清理 <br />\n但唔識讀又會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過如果講到呢兩句確實意思+識讀+明確立場<br />\n都應該有4-5以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249d92c8bcbabd6f840b7884ec1965a51c2deeca","tid":158201,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:22:11.000Z","msg":"日本仲有「滌溺器」呢項活動，目的係克服自身污穢，洗滌心靈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a96b6d61a46c06f14efc71a8dadd19c44ceb2c","tid":158201,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:22:26.000Z","msg":"中文老師都做唔到既卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本