,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:59:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水 火 人<br />\n<br />\n先係口試題既極致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有屋企人alevel中呢條A左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecdb0e34653416b4210a32ec549ec272e0fad8d5","tid":158201,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:02:11.000Z","msg":"「戲彩娛親」個故事就好似聽過<br />\n「滌親溺器」又係乜春故事黎<br />\n呢兩樣又有咩可比性<br />\nR晒頭"},{"pid":"3bd4678b67cb42c51fb41ea3455ead92bec381b8","tid":158201,"uid":52591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:02:43.000Z","msg":"識，如果考攞硬5<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438862f9cb89b234f5d04ab665102440a0a833ad","tid":158201,"uid":19464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:03:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌真係好撚煩<br />\n成日都講到呢d題目最撚難咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只不過係因為隻成語唔識 但係資料明明有解釋清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真就咁比題目就嚇得下人姐 大把大學生都唔識解 但佢資料有比解釋囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講番孝道就正常中學生都識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:考呢題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n期待你既成績</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n資料又有冇提個故事背景啊<br />\n又有冇諗過你個論點未必match返照仆得街<br />\nlm睇3都未必有,講到孝道好似得一樣野,咁仲洗撚比兩件事你比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n脷伸:23先考,eaa咪係我個題玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你班人柒少陣啦<br />\n明知報紙佬最鍾意誇大嚟講點難點難<br />\n有人講個事實出嚟就轉移視線問人地有無5**<br />\n佢本身可能無5**水平但呢條點都係一條正常題目<br />\n正常嘅考生點都會發揮到自己水平好難失手<br />\n自己廢就唔好以為其他人同你地一樣廢<br />\n題目補充資料入面係有出曬成個故事來龍去脈解釋得清清楚楚"},{"pid":"15b75d5268d32b25e5958fc0e9c14a8af885042e","tid":158201,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:06:15.000Z","msg":"玩難字<br />\n宜家玩use of Chinese<br />\n定係 變左 Chinese studies?<br />\n<br />\n 相信好多人考中文係為左pass 又或者4左右<br />\n點解要雕難考生<br />\n<br />\n出題果班廢老廢中真係禍國殃民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b30a62e0d3fe29698ab6c30519ee81cfba67c7d","tid":158201,"uid":54730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:14:41.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得呢題幾好講<br />\n雖然個字係有d難讀 但其實本身條題目唔難<br />\n仲要個題目本身有解釋"},{"pid":"79125d54aaedf65064f5b56116e15cc77aa7c4ae","tid":158201,"uid":13351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"（洗）滌親（人）（便）溺（的）器（具）<br />\n加啲關聯字會易理解好多<br />\n<br />\n利申中文u<br />\n<br />\n不過正常人有時都會執筆忘字同讀錯音啦，莫講話考生"},{"pid":"a435fbd114c979f523b24e47f1c4d392a228ab97","tid":158201,"uid":54730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:18:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實都係考個討論技巧，討論下學校應唔應該推xxx既政策 之類咪夠<br />\n<br />\n仲要一日有幾條問題，條條難度差好遠，又一齊拉curve，根本唔公平</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前個年考個題<br />\n本身題目唔難 有五個選擇<br />\n點知要排序仲要達成共識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一年出屌打曬d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好唔公平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d67f4208d07b4c24d4f42663c76dca4fa7fb06","tid":158201,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:19:51.000Z","msg":"呢兩個我唔識<br />\n但係屌你老母我就識啦"},{"pid":"59c6ae56220bd9498b4db2ff54a62285be65d67e","tid":158201,"uid":72203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:21:34.000Z","msg":"唔係就係24孝故事咩...難係邊.."},{"pid":"19041470c1ecf602b54adddce9b99130b240a238","tid":158201,"uid":71000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:23:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學文憑試中文科一直被喻為「死亡之卷」，不少牙尖嘴利的考生以為可以在說話能力考卷搶回不少分數，但昨日的口試題目卻驚現廿四孝故事典故題，要考生討論「戲彩娛親」、「滌親溺器」哪個提倡孝道的故事更值得為人子女者學習，頓時考起學生，有考生直言：「個四字詞讀都未識讀」，認為題目太深，學生難以發揮。 <br />\n<br />\n「戲彩娛親」、「滌親溺器」說的是甚麼故事？題目附有解釋，指「戲彩娛親」是指「穿上斑斕的五彩衣裳，裝作小孩形態，戲耍舞蹈，娛悅雙親為樂」；「滌親溺器」則解作「每天晚上都親自為母親清洗便桶」。若非滿肚墨水可清楚解釋故事內容，恐怕亦難以作出精彩辯論搶分。 <br />\n<br />\n有考生看過題目後，直言：「兩個故事都唔識」，應考時「口啞啞」，擔心會嚴重失分；有考生更稱，在解釋「滌親溺器」時，「我講果陣原本想讀「迪」(滌粵音為迪)，但係(同組考生)讀咗「條」，搞到我怯一怯跟咗佢，最後成組錯晒。」<span style=\"color: red;\">有考生則指：「有人話幫母親洗尿兜好唔衞生，唔應該滌親溺器，笑死。」 </span><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩問題？笑人果個應該唔識點做依款題目 9成fail硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0413a77d65a205af5fe6daecae5a9b1bba6f6c2a","tid":158201,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:28:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62014838ded56acdb9bb0e1d7c6ead2439d8ff70","tid":158201,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下年見"},{"pid":"c1889b7e053dd70db7b4ded0a254d5be89bdceba","tid":158201,"uid":82940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:37:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌真係好撚煩<br />\n成日都講到呢d題目最撚難咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只不過係因為隻成語唔識 但係資料明明有解釋清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真就咁比題目就嚇得下人姐 大把大學生都唔識解 但佢資料有比解釋囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講番孝道就正常中學生都識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:考呢題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/fac